plainTextMessage.value: With the COVID-19 situation lingering that limits physical interaction and collaboration, it is timely to explore other forms of engagement with our clients and users since it will take some time before things can return to normalcy. Hence, apart from showcasing different advanced technology adoption and innovation in Jabil Digital Lab, we intend to implement an interactive web application that virtualises the Jabil Digital Lab located in Singapore. This interactive web application or Digital Factory 2.0 (DF2.0) shall leverage on best-of-breed web design and digital reality technologies to give the users a unique experience.
